creator: EarthSoft, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
EQuIS Collect is a new EarthSoft application that allows you to collect any data on your phone, tablet, or PC. It works easily offline when you don't have internet access in remote areas.

Use your EQuIS Credentials to login and access our large form library. Once you collect data on your selected form you can push saved forms from EDP to EQuIS. You can even view the form status on Collect (received, accepted, rejected, completed).

Collecting non-EQuIS data? Not a problem. Our app collects any data!

Features

- Collect any data
- Device agnostic (phone, tablet, PC)
- Supports all major operating systems
- Subscription licensing
- Use any EQuIS EDD formats integrating with EQuIS workflows
- EQuIS Enterprise Form Builder with EDP checks and validation
- Deploy Collect forms instantly to end users in the field
- View Forms status and reports in real-time on EQuIS Collect and Enterprise
descriptionShort: Collect any data easily in the field on phones, tablets, or PCs
